 Broad understanding of hardware and software installation and troubleshooting in a desktop computing environment 
 Proven ability to implement strategies which deliver business benefit and measurable, actionable results. 
 Experience with IT Service Desk technologies and platforms 
 Advanced knowledge of ITIL frameworks for service delivery and service support processes 
 Ability to create new ways of solving problems, improving efficiencies and implementing value-driven technical and service solutions. 
